trans-unit.source: Contains settings that <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicValue%601> and <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicReference%601> instances use to compile the source text of the expressions they contain.
trans-unit.target: 包含設定的<xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicValue%601>和<xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicReference%601>用來編譯所包含之運算式的來源文字的執行個體。

trans-unit.source: These settings include assembly references and imported namespaces required to compile an expression.
trans-unit.target: 這些設定包括組件參考和匯入編譯運算式所需的命名空間。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicSettings"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新執行個體<xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicSettings"></xref>類別。

trans-unit.source: Gets a <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicSettings"></xref> that contains the default set of assembly references and imported namespaces.
trans-unit.target: 取得<xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicSettings"> </xref> ，其中包含組件參考和匯入命名空間的預設設定。

trans-unit.source: This set is available to all <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicValue%601> and <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicReference%601> instances in a given <xref href="System.AppDomain"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 這個集合是可供所有<xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicValue%601>和<xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicReference%601>中執行個體指定<xref href="System.AppDomain"> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: The following table lists the default imported namespaces and assembly references.
trans-unit.target: 下表列出預設的匯入命名空間和組件參考。

|匯入命名空間 |組件 | |------------------------|--------------| |系統 | mscorlib | |系統 |系統 | |System.Collections|mscorlib| |System.Collections.Generic|mscorlib| |System.Collections.Generic|系統 | |System.Activities|System.Activities| |System.Activities.Statements|System.Activities| |System.Activities.Expressions|System.Activities|

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicSettings"></xref> that contains the default set of assembly references and imported namespaces.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicSettings"> </xref> ，其中包含組件參考和匯入命名空間的預設設定。

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference"></xref> objects, each of which represents an assembly reference and a namespace imported from that assembly.
trans-unit.target: 取得集合的<xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference"></xref>物件，其中每一個都表示一個組件參考和該組件從匯入的命名空間。

trans-unit.source: A collection of <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference"></xref> objects, each of which represents an assembly reference and a namespace imported from that assembly.
trans-unit.target: 集合<xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference"></xref>物件，其中每一個都表示一個組件參考和該組件從匯入的命名空間。
